The '''Battle of Althir''' can refer to two separate battles that occurred during the [[Mandalorian Wars]]:
*The first [[Battle of Althir (first)|Battle of Althir]] was a naval engagement fought over [[Althir III]] in [[3976 BBY]], the first battle of the Mandalorian Wars.
*The second battle, also known as the [[Battle of Althir (second)|Battle of Althir]], was a ground battle around [[3960 BBY]] that saw the annihilation of most of the [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorian]] ground forces.
